a.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 171}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer's games\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 194}, {\"ngram\": \"a whopping 121 medals\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 265}, {\"ngram\": \"39 gold\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"nearest rivals\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time of writing on day six they have made a great start winning 31 medals, including six golds to put them way out in front in the medal table - at least that's what US media would tell you.\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 6.299314829913161e-13, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 345}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 363}, {\"ngram\": \"a great start\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 396}, {\"ngram\": \"31 medals\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"six golds\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal table\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reality is they are currently only fifth in the table, behind China, France, Japan and Australia.Great Britain are narrowly behind in sixth.\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 677, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 599, \"end\": 604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.687792529959762, \"rank\": 0.3289375072252523, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_fo